data.value: Sister to Nathaniel Nutmeg. 'Naughty' Nelly Nutmeg is known around town as a promiscous girl with her head in the clouds. We wouldn't have asked her questions, if it weren't for her talkin' about Nathaniel's claims against Bill Bourbon. According to Nelly, her brother Nathaniel would talk about how Bourbon's business chain was taking over small businesses. Nathaniel had told her that Bourbon was planning on opening a new bar that could put him out of business. Nelly claims that her brother would never hurt a fly, but she also mentioned that she overheard him talk about Burbon's drinkin problem, and wondered if he had ever tried to push sales a little to far.
